{"id":562188,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/06/辽宁省监狱管理局违法了/","date":"2017-06-27T00:26:27Z","modified":"2017-06-27T06:01:30Z","title":"【立此存照】辽宁省监狱管理局违法了","content":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>2017年6月26日，辽宁省监狱管理局发布消息：</p>\n<h3></h3>\n<h3>刘晓波因病被批准保外就医</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>辽宁省锦州监狱服刑人员刘晓波，近期被诊断患有肝癌。近日，辽宁省监狱管理局依法批准刘晓波保外就医。中国医科大学附属第一医院已组成由8位国内知名肿瘤专家参加的医疗救治小组，制定了治疗方案。刘晓波正在按医疗方案接受治疗。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-562209\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/1-48-300x165.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"325\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/1-48-300x165.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/1-48-768x422.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/1-48-1024x563.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/1-48.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>网民发现：辽宁省监狱管理局发布的刘晓波患病治疗信息，网易新闻收录了。有朋友转发到微博去，结果——违法了。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-562212\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/IMG_2254-169x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"1049\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/IMG_2254-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/IMG_2254-576x1024.jpg 576w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/IMG_2254.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>随后，网易新闻也“页面丢失啦”。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-562213\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/IMG_2256-225x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"787\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/IMG_2256-225x300.png 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/IMG_2256-768x1024.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/IMG_2256.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" /></p>\n","author":1052,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[9041,32959,32957,23072,9006,14804,14431,32961]}